  "rampMode.infoTitle": "Ramp mode",
  "rampMode.infoBody": "Ramping smooths abrupt position or gain changes so object motion and level updates stay more natural and produce fewer clicks or spatial jumps.<br /><br /><strong>Off</strong>: disable interpolation and jump immediately to the new target.<br /><br /><strong>Per frame</strong>: apply one interpolation step per decoded audio frame. This is lighter and more stepped.<br /><br /><strong>Per sample</strong>: apply one interpolation step for every rendered sample. This is the smoothest mode.",
