  "effectiveRender.infoButton": "Effective render info",
  "effectiveRender.infoBody": "Shows an estimated effective render position computed from the current speaker gains.<br><br>A small marker is placed at the weighted centroid of the active speakers, using a power-style weighting based on each gain squared.<br><br>The thin line connects the object's nominal position to this effective rendered position.",
